@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dbvgco(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = (0.18 + wp.abs(0.15))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp))
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.09)) - (0.96 * wp.abs(tmp + 0.10)))
    v2 = 0.93
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.72) * (v1 + 0.50 + v0 + 0.20)) - 0.64)
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
